{"tid":2463804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉淑儀：支持新疆棉　但毋須特意破壞現有產品","createTime":"2021-03-27T03:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T04:00:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c82ae611e8005dc6a15937aebbbfa7dc4fe2abe","tid":2463804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:52:20.000Z","msg":"全國人大常委會將於下星期一及二開會，審議修改《基本法》附件一及二，修改特首及立法會的選舉辦法。行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀形容本港政治藍圖將會重新劃分，相信直選議席中，建制派會取得一半數目。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀在一個電台節目表示，相信屆時將會公布立法會90個議席如何分布，選委會在立法會將佔較大比例。她又說，現時社會怨氣高，相信仍會有素人出來參選，議會內依然有反對聲音。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀在節目後表示，修改選舉辦法對新民黨有正面影響，希望下屆選舉能維持兩個議席。<br />\n<br />\n另外，她日前在社交平台宣布停買及停用牽涉「新疆棉風波」的品牌產品，被問到是否會有進一步行動，她認為不需要，因主要是希望品牌可收回聲明及道歉，不覺得要特意去破壞一些現有的產品。<br />\n<br />\n對於國台辦發言人點名稱讚她在一場外媒主辦的研討會上，離場抗議有與會者指「台灣是國家」，葉劉淑儀說，出席研討會前，不知道同場有「台獨分子」，她感謝國台辦的讚揚，形容是無意的收穫。"},{"pid":"d6446e019cc8414ca595280573630ac79e80601b","tid":2463804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/aa6709260fd120fc0f48cfe140472542/2021/03/36488a5a7f411da6562942e24c54c8df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2Faa6709260fd120fc0f48cfe140472542%2F2021%2F03%2F36488a5a7f411da6562942e24c54c8df.jpg&h=35a1f9cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582881-20210327.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582881-20210327.htm&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=56457cf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582881-20210327.htm&h=3e067772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582881-20210327.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4a22830b66b39edf511f4d3be1dd93685d16ff0a","tid":2463804,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"假愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0466922b992a2ebd177a1a1ae259964a25537c24","tid":2463804,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426aead92b34378dd2102865278d519f19bfc07d","tid":2463804,"uid":238920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:54:23.000Z","msg":"同班黃絲借機抵制藍營有咩分別<br />\n做生意還做生意,政治還政治<br />\n葉劉係咪又想搞顏色革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2494fb5dac7e879ca4c0751988b092019a94ec","tid":2463804,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:56:43.000Z","msg":"嚴正聲明<br />\n<br />\n本人所用的產品均為假貨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb24284cae351c38ee65e56549a19af18de57c99","tid":2463804,"uid":305358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:58:03.000Z","msg":"毋須特意破壞現有產品 = 包庇窩藏罪犯<br />\n<br />\n罪大惡極！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2c9ff810075ad79bc2093a6548cfcb4733ceec","tid":2463804,"uid":61745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"佢個樣根本係忍住唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}